    <div class="sl">Why It Matters</div>
    <h2>Scent Is Your Hotel's <em>Silent Ambassador</em></h2>
    <p class="lead">The world's most beloved hotel brands have invested in signature scents for decades because they know what neuroscience confirms: the smell of your lobby is the most powerful memory anchor your guests will take home. It outperforms your décor, your music, your views — and shapes whether guests rebook, recommend, and remember.</p>
