    <h2>Scenting Every Zone of Your <em>Property</em></h2>
    <div class="zones">
      <div class="zone"><h4>Lobby &amp; Reception</h4><p>The signature impression. Custom fragrance development designed to embody your brand identity and welcome every guest.</p></div>
      <div class="zone"><h4>Guest Suites</h4><p>Refined room programs that elevate the in-suite experience without overwhelming. Premium linen sprays and ambient diffusion.</p></div>
      <div class="zone"><h4>Spa &amp; Wellness</h4><p>Therapy-supporting scents for treatment rooms, relaxation lounges, and pool decks. Wellness-aligned formulations.</p></div>
      <div class="zone"><h4>Dining &amp; Bars</h4><p>Subtle complementary scenting for restaurants and lounges that enhances atmosphere without competing with food aromas.</p></div>
      <div class="zone"><h4>Meeting &amp; Event Spaces</h4><p>Energizing or calming scents calibrated for corporate events, weddings, and private functions.</p></div>
      <div class="zone"><h4>Corridors &amp; Elevators</h4><p>Thread-consistency scenting that maintains brand atmosphere as guests move throughout the property.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="sl">Our Process</div>
    <h2>From Discovery to <em>Deployment</em></h2>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-num">01</div><h3>Property Assessment</h3><p>We visit your property to understand your guest journey, brand identity, architecture, and HVAC system. Every recommendation is tailored to your unique space.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-num">02</div><h3>Scent Strategy</h3><p>Custom scent profiles for each zone. Choose from our premium library or commission a fully bespoke signature fragrance for your brand.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-num">03</div><h3>System Design</h3><p>Professional cold-air or HVAC-integrated diffusion systems engineered for your coverage requirements. Whisper-quiet, programmable, energy-efficient.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-num">04</div><h3>Installation</h3><p>Our certified team handles installation with minimal property disruption. Most boutique properties go live within 2-3 days.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-num">05</div><h3>Ongoing Support</h3><p>Subscription fragrance refills, system maintenance, and seasonal scent rotations. Your property never runs out of atmosphere.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-num">06</div><h3>Performance Review</h3><p>Quarterly check-ins to evaluate guest feedback, refine intensity, and ensure your scent program continues delivering measurable impact.</p></div>
    </div>
